### What audio equipment do you need for a wedding?

A standard wedding setup includes:

1\. A PA system for announcements and speeches  
2\. Wireless microphones for the officiant and speakers  
3\. Background music player capability  
4\. DJ system for the reception

****Malaga Event Gear (MEG)**** has a comprehensive inventory to cover all these needs and more, tailored to fit your wedding size and venue.

